en_42363_0	Three persons have died following electrocution.
en_42363_1	The incident has occurred in the Thalahagama as at Gonakamulla in Akuressa.
en_42363_2	They have died due to an illegal electric cable.
en_42363_3	The Office of the Police Media Spokesman said that inquiries have been launched following information received by the Akuressa Police.
en_42363_4	The deceased are all males aged 45, 56 and 76.
en_42363_5	All of them are residents of Thalahagama.
en_42363_6	The electrocution had taken place at around 7.30 this morning.
